plyTime":"2019-08-26T20:58:30.000Z","msg":"你仲洗唔洗靠屋企養？唔洗就開佢波，起碼同佢地講唔搬返深水埗冇資格同你討論警察做得啱定錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T21:02:56.000Z","msg":"其實我最近研究緊 開波嘅話一定會更加鬧得激烈 咁如果用「人人對我我對人人呢」<br />\n用大愛模式 好好心咁樣同佢講成件事 同埋解釋清楚 雖然畀著我我都會選擇開波 但我覺得大愛模式好似仲好過開波 起碼有機率可以令到藍絲轉黃絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T21:05:05.000Z","msg":"深藍既人，你用鐵筆打開佢個頭會簡單好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淺藍既咪叫佢返深水埗感覺下警察執法有幾公正囉"},{"pid":"b39b04fcb0e33b01633ea01ff18cd47475f5fa24","tid":1509333,"uid":147895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T21:07:37.000Z","msg":"試下用斧頭開雞蛋，菜刀炒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfec584ad083ec7a0faf1b789d13901885d32faf","tid":1509333,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T21:12:20.000Z","msg":"下次叫外賣"},{"pid":"c0d8f02cb7cb2215636f274bcd1a8f94ac3851ec","tid":1509333,"uid":217548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfec584ad083ec7a0faf1b789d13901885d32faf","tid":1509333,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T21:12:20.000Z","msg":"下次叫外賣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T21:19:20.000Z","msg":"其實每次啲警察一咁做 所有食肆都會關門<br />\n樓下嗰間 m記已經好早關咗門 跟住711 個阿姐藍絲到飛起 一見到發生呢啲事即刻關門 所以我想講我最後就算如果落咗街都係冇嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd25940e449aba9fd0222e2c18b42b50495a654d","tid":1509333,"uid":210956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T22:00:00.000Z","msg":"先利申街坊<br />\n<br />\n好明白你感受..<br />\n啲狗癲到搜埋內街, 追人追到石硤尾,<br />\n仲要今次親耳聽到畜膿講野有鄉音<br />\n巴打你仲要係樓下大門都出